[
  {
    "text": "Shloka Kini: The authentication context is a web service ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=1"
  },
  {
    "text": "that presents the authentication UI ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=3"
  },
  {
    "text": "and communicates with your identity provider server ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=5"
  },
  {
    "text": "to authenticate your customer's credentials.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=8"
  },
  {
    "text": "It is one of many steps you will need to take ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=11"
  },
  {
    "text": "to get the Single Sign-On feature for your TV provider ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=13"
  },
  {
    "text": "on iOS and tvOS devices ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=16"
  },
  {
    "text": "as part of the Apple TV distribution program.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=19"
  },
  {
    "text": "The authentication context is a web service ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=22"
  },
  {
    "text": "hosted on your server that is downloaded to an Apple device ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=24"
  },
  {
    "text": "and executed at run time.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=28"
  },
  {
    "text": "When the authentication context ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=30"
  },
  {
    "text": "passes an authentication response ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=32"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the VideoSubscriberAccount framework ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=34"
  },
  {
    "text": "it is saved into the device keychain.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=36"
  },
  {
    "text": "On iOS devices the authentication response ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=38"
  },
  {
    "text": "can be synced to other iOS devices via iCloud Keychain.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=41"
  },
  {
    "text": "And on Apple TV, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=45"
  },
  {
    "text": "the authentication response will not leave the device ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=47"
  },
  {
    "text": "because tvOS does not support iCloud Keychain.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=49"
  },
  {
    "text": "The purpose of the authentication context ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=53"
  },
  {
    "text": "is to provide OS-level authentication ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=55"
  },
  {
    "text": "across supported apps.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=58"
  },
  {
    "text": "The first step of this process is to prompt a person ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=60"
  },
  {
    "text": "to type in their credentials ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=62"
  },
  {
    "text": "by presenting them UI for authentication.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=64"
  },
  {
    "text": "To specify the UI for this credential entry, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=67"
  },
  {
    "text": "use an authenticationTemplate.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=70"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is an XML document ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=72"
  },
  {
    "text": "similar to the examples we provide in documentation.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=74"
  },
  {
    "text": "When you provide us this XML, we take it and format it ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=77"
  },
  {
    "text": "to look like part of the Apple system UI, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=81"
  },
  {
    "text": "depending on which platform the person is using.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=83"
  },
  {
    "text": "For example, the default username-password template here, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=86"
  },
  {
    "text": "can be applied to both iOS and tvOS devices.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=89"
  },
  {
    "text": "The autoAuthenticationTemplate doesn't ask the customer ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=95"
  },
  {
    "text": "to enter credentials.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=98"
  },
  {
    "text": "Instead, it informs the customer ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=99"
  },
  {
    "text": "which account they will be automatically authenticated to, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=101"
  },
  {
    "text": "and gives them an option to manually sign in ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=104"
  },
  {
    "text": "to a different account.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=107"
  },
  {
    "text": "This template is also applicable to both iOS and tvOS devices.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=109"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you are not able to directly take credentials ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=115"
  },
  {
    "text": "from a customer, we provide alternative templates ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=117"
  },
  {
    "text": "for authentication in special cases.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=120"
  },
  {
    "text": "The onscreenCode AuthenticationTemplate ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=123"
  },
  {
    "text": "only applies to tvOS.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=125"
  },
  {
    "text": "It displays an onscreen code for a person to enter ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=127"
  },
  {
    "text": "on a web browser on a separate device, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=130"
  },
  {
    "text": "such as their phone, tablet, or computer.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=132"
  },
  {
    "text": "The webAuthenticationTemplate applies only to iOS devices.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=136"
  },
  {
    "text": "It launches a web view, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=140"
  },
  {
    "text": "like this, using the URL specified.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=142"
  },
  {
    "text": "To communicate between the authentication context ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=145"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the web view that is launched, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=148"
  },
  {
    "text": "you use the VideoSubscriberAccount class.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=150"
  },
  {
    "text": "To get started, you will create an authentication context ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=153"
  },
  {
    "text": "with JavaScript and define the authentication UI ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=156"
  },
  {
    "text": "with XML templates.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=159"
  },
  {
    "text": "Host this JavaScript file on your server.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=160"
  },
  {
    "text": "Remember only to write one authentication context, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=163"
  },
  {
    "text": "because the same one can be used for both devices.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=166"
  },
  {
    "text": "Lastly, after writing your context and XML, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=169"
  },
  {
    "text": "send us the TV provider onboarding data.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=173"
  },
  {
    "text": "This data includes the name to be displayed in our UI ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=176"
  },
  {
    "text": "for the TV provider; ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=179"
  },
  {
    "text": "the identifier for the TV provider, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=181"
  },
  {
    "text": "which will be used in our systems ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=183"
  },
  {
    "text": "to identify the TV provider uniquely amongst others; ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=185"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the authentication URL, the URL we need to ping ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=188"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the TV provider server to access and download ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=191"
  },
  {
    "text": "your authentication context to device.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=194"
  },
  {
    "text": "Send us the artwork to be displayed ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=197"
  },
  {
    "text": "for the TV provider's brand in the App Store UI.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=199"
  },
  {
    "text": "For more details on the artwork specs, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=202"
  },
  {
    "text": "see our documentation.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=204"
  },
  {
    "text": "Send us a supported channel list.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=206"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is an optional piece of onboarding data.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=207"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here, a channel references TV provider-supported apps.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=210"
  },
  {
    "text": "In the Apple TV distribution program, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=214"
  },
  {
    "text": "one app will be automatically installed ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=216"
  },
  {
    "text": "after the authentication flow; that's the main app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=218"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you have any additional apps ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=221"
  },
  {
    "text": "that use your TV provider credentials, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=223"
  },
  {
    "text": "use this list to show those other TV provider-supported apps ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=225"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the customer.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=229"
  },
  {
    "text": "To begin developing the authentication context, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=231"
  },
  {
    "text": "handle the callbacks for requests ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=234"
  },
  {
    "text": "made by the VideoSubscriberAccount framework ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=236"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the authentication context.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=238"
  },
  {
    "text": "The first is onLaunch.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=240"
  },
  {
    "text": "This indicates what should happen after a TV provider ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=243"
  },
  {
    "text": "is selected from the VideoSubscriberAccount list.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=246"
  },
  {
    "text": "After selecting a TV provider, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=249"
  },
  {
    "text": "a pending screen appears until the next callback.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=251"
  },
  {
    "text": "onShowUserInterface.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=254"
  },
  {
    "text": "After launch, then you must handle the callback ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=257"
  },
  {
    "text": "to show the authentication template for credential entry.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=260"
  },
  {
    "text": "Next is onRequest.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=264"
  },
  {
    "text": "After credentials are entered, you take those credentials ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=267"
  },
  {
    "text": "and send them directly to your identity provider server.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=270"
  },
  {
    "text": "These credentials are not stored on device.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=273"
  },
  {
    "text": "An authentication response is sent back from the server ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=275"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the authentication context ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=278"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the VideoSubscriberAccount framework ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=280"
  },
  {
    "text": "to establish system-level authentication.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=282"
  },
  {
    "text": "App-level authentication requests ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=285"
  },
  {
    "text": "will only be sent for processing ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=286"
  },
  {
    "text": "if this system-level authentication is good.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=288"
  },
  {
    "text": "To debug your application, enable Developer Mode ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=291"
  },
  {
    "text": "on your iOS and tvOS devices ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=294"
  },
  {
    "text": "to add and test your TV provider before code is live.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=297"
  },
  {
    "text": "To specifically debug your authentication context, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=301"
  },
  {
    "text": "use Safari Web Inspector.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=303"
  },
  {
    "text": "Make sure to enable Web Inspector on device ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=305"
  },
  {
    "text": "so your macOS device can debug the JavaScript.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=308"
  },
  {
    "text": "In summary, the authentication context ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=312"
  },
  {
    "text": "is a JavaScript-based web service ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=314"
  },
  {
    "text": "that facilitates communication ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=316"
  },
  {
    "text": "between the identity provider server for a TV provider ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=317"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the VideoSubscriberAccount framework.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=320"
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-505/?time=323"
  }
]